headline: Phillips 66 Board Members Glenn Tilton and Marna Whittington Announce Intention to Retire
summary: HOUSTON, October 23, 2025--Phillips 66 announced that Glenn Tilton and Marna Whittington intend to retire and will not stand for re-election to the company board of directors.
